"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"**What’s the future of social media?**\\n\\nMy hope is that it becomes more decentralized over time. When social networks buy other social networks to become networks of networks, I don’t think that’s healthy for society. \\n\\nPendulums tend to swing too far in one direction and then eventually get pushed back hard in the other. On one hand, giving everyone a platform has made for a period of incredible innovation and connectivity and has weakened the gatekeepers. On the other hand, algorithms and pick-your-own-news sources have a tendency to pull people into echo chambers and contribute to polarization in society.\\n\\nA large part of the rise of mega-corporations over the past decade is a result of benefiting from user data and making users the product rather than the customer. Google and Facebook did this abundantly by\",\"timestamp\":1639216254,\"title\":\"a senior statistician from the National Bureau of Statistics\"},\"digest\":\"_iligqA7T3XvviJJUj5BOosSPe0fAijYi88NiCT8NKU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xAC44205b7fe86d562466F41cC9a8051488cFd8A7\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3lFYrjkEKXLtH6ia47aqindEnP-T8G8QNpKjWlo3fFo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"krdHmrK-mlUoKK-GQnd8-U-wbpIzW2G69Uz0tu6qql8\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"qslfCXJUAxj_jmrrx_jFKxIlU6X10fQvgFBLO6ktAI9CVoC9ilHzfmtZfyzdtzFA56ypuHpHknLAaszw3pivqA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe40af8f41000604fa516ff94fa94b1593b649eb4e8009ab661d91f70a1ebb8815d60947ec610f065d24ac0b8124690c2f8fbdd983d4183d740df7823477521cc1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"3lFYrjkEKXLtH6ia47aqindEnP-T8G8QNpKjWlo3fFo\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"krdHmrK-mlUoKK-GQnd8-U-wbpIzW2G69Uz0tu6qql8\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"vers